{"tid":636834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過馬路畀車撞　馬來西亞消防員助7米巨蟒返屋企","createTime":"2018-04-21T09:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T10:05:31.000Z","uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80b288ab7d539b47392d8701fc2c8dcc6e314aee","tid":636834,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/171334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F171334_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a60a7d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞彭亨關丹一條7米長、重100公斤的大蟒蛇，周四（19日）橫跨馬路時遭車輛撞傷，消防局接報後派員到場將牠帶走。大蛇身體狀況非常虛弱，消防員將牠交給半島野生動物保護及國家公園局，待牠康復後再放返大自然。 <br />\n<br />\n消防局副總監莫哈末沙尼表示，他們原本打算把蛇趕至附近的森林，但由於牠受傷了，只好把牠帶走。大蛇體型龐大及受傷關係，8名消防員花逾一小時，才成功將牠捕獲。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/mobile/bknint-20180421030023294-0421_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20180421030023294-0421_17011_001.html&d=fchuQbFKY0nEdUBkMLtXEtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=08c5bc71\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/mobile/bknint-20180421030023294-0421_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"759b89bcd0ba46fdfe129ca6e5693e6082e56ddd","tid":636834,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fae98aa14dfcdf7651d4b869c2c1f5f5d3ab869","tid":636834,"uid":31920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"補身"},{"pid":"212b5aac41183eed9869738b46cd13ea1c147e96","tid":636834,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T10:05:31.000Z","msg":"大蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}